title: Friday News Rundown with Steve Wyche

description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler and Steve Wyche break down all of the latest news in the NFL. Marc Sessler talks about getting lost in the mountains for hours.
